item.description: This is the beginning of your journey with me. We both have vitiligo or white spots so I know how you feel. I was compelled to go deeper, so I became a holistic nutritionist to get to the root cause. Follow my path as I learn and share what I learn with you so that together we can stop the frustration and heal through nutrition. Are you ready? I'll be with you every step of the way ;-)
